 is directed by acclaimed filmmakers and Shrek franchise veterans Conrad Vernon and Walt Dohrn. Vernon was a member of the directing team on the Academy Award\u00AE nominated Shrek 2 as well as on DreamWorks Animation\u2019s Madagascar 3: Europe\u2019s Most Wanted and Monsters vs. Aliens. Vernon has also provided the voice of Shrek fan-favorite Gingerbread Man, aka \u201CGingy,\u201D across all titles in the Shrek Universe. Dohrn worked on the second and third Shrek films as a writer and artist and as Head of Story on the fourth film. Dohrn also voiced the character of Rumpelstiltskin in Shrek Forever After. Dohrn served as co-director on the first Trolls film and directed Trolls World Tour and Trolls Band Together. \n\nThe film is produced by returning producer Gina Shay (Trolls franchise), who produced Shrek Forever After and by Illumination CEO and Academy Award\u00AE nominee Chris Meledandri (the Super Mario, Despicable Me and Minions franchises). The film is co-directed by Brad Ableson (Minions: The Rise of Gru, The Simpsons).\n\nSocial Handles\nInstagram: https://www.instagram.com/shrek/\nFacebook: https://www.facebook.com/Shrek/\nX: https://twitter.com/shrek \nThreads: https://www.threads.com/@shrek\nTikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@shrek\nOfficial Site: https://www.Shrek.com","ChannelId":"UCq0OueAsdxH6b8nyAspwViw","ChannelTitle":"Universal Pictures","ThumbnailUrl":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/Swiz1XyfhcI/mqdefault.jpg","ViewCount":2161664,"LikeCount":62032,"CommentCount":0,"PublishedAt":"2026-06-16T15:00:03Z","Category":"24","GapScore":0.7,"DemandScore":0.9,"CompetitionScore":1,"TrendScore":0.9},{"VideoId":"4IE_PQaG7xk","Title":"FREE GRIDIRON OTIS AND JAE-YONG!","Description":"\u26BD\uFE0F\uFE0F adidas STARR CUP IS ON! \u26BD\uFE0F\n\nThe entire Community will be split into two for the first football Community Event! Reach the Grand Final and face off against the other half of the community to become CHAMPIONS \uD83D\uDC51\n\nTEAM CREATION\n\uD83D\uDC5F Vote for y